  <brief_title>Use of Topical Budesonide in the Treatment of Eosinophilic Esophagitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Topical Budesonide in the Treatment of Eosinophilic Esophagitis, a Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
